This paper discusses the use of word embeddings in natural language processing and the issue of bias in these embeddings. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
